    "body": "that's what I use to fix it in my build:\r\n#for grpc 1.3.x and above (1.6.x now): fix soname and filename inconsistency for libgrpc++*.so.N\r\nsed -i.bak -e \"s|libgrpc++\\([^\\.]*\\)\\.so\\.[0-9]|libgrpc++\\1.so.1|g\" Makefile\r\n"
